\myparagraph{Measuring retrieval effectiveness} To evaluate retrieval quality, we use answer presence as our metric. It is a binary measure of whether one of the gold answers is present in the top-{{arxiv_2204_11677_FO0094||FO}} evidences ({{arxiv_2204_11677_FO0095||FO}} in all experiments).